Source: ebox-webserver
Section: web
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Enrique J. Hernandez <quique@warp.es>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 4.0.0)
Standards-Version: 3.6.1

Package: ebox-webserver
Architecture: all
Depends: ebox (== 0.10.99), ebox-firewall, apache2
Conflicts: ebox (<< 0.10.99)
Description: Web Server
 eBox is a framework for the development and deployment of security-wise
 network services in small and medium-sized networks, offering a simplified
 graphical interface to non expert users. It can be set up as a gateway,
 having some extra features over a usual router.
 .
 This module adds a web server to eBox, allowing publication of contents
 using several virtual hosts and using userdir module.
